      <title>Adnoc 以 40 亿美元交易首次登陆债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/adnoc-debuts-on-bond-market-with-three-tranche-dollar-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比主要石油生产商阿布扎比国家石油公司 (Adnoc) 计划通过首次发行债券筹集 40 亿美元，加入全球范围内的债券发行热潮，企业希望锁定优惠的借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/adnoc-debuts-on-bond-market-with-three-tranche-dollar-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:33:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金抹去损失，因美国就业数据疲软增强降息预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/gold-steady-near-2-500-as-traders-take-stock-after-market-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国就业岗位数据进一步表明劳动力市场正在降温，为美联储很快开始降低借贷成本奠定了基础，黄金价格抹去了早前的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/gold-steady-near-2-500-as-traders-take-stock-after-market-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
